videos.title: Death Digletts Needed Zetalpa
videos.description:
The Urborg Scavengers (aka Death Digletts) might've given Zetalpa it's first chance of being semi playable! It's a keyword soup playstyle reminiscent of Soulflayer.

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkigndom.com/mtggoldfish
